Module kivakit.core.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.data.comparison

Class Differences

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.data.comparison.Differences
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Countable, Sized
    public class Differences
extends java.lang.Object
implements Sized
    Tracks the difference between objects that are compared with compare(String, Object, Object) or compare(String, Iterable, Iterable). If there have been any differences, isDifferent() will return true, and if not, isIdentical() will return true. The number of differences is available through size() and toString() returns a description of all the differences that have been encountered.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
